  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together flour, baking powder, and sugar.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together egg, milk, and fromage frais.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Heat an iron teppan over medium heat.",
    " grease the teppan with butter.",
    "Drop the batter by 1/4 cupfuls onto the teppan.",
    "Cook the pancakes for 2-3 minutes, until bubbles appear on the surface and the edges start to dry.",
    "Flip the pancakes and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until golden brown.",
    "Repeat with the remaining batter, greasing the teppan with butter as needed.",
    "Serve the pancakes hot with lacquer glaze (see below)."
